n = int(input())
a = list(map(int, input().split()))
for i in range(n):
    m = i
    for j in range(i + 1, n):
        if a[j] < a[m]:
            m = j
    a[i], a[m] = a[m], a[i]
print(*a)

n = int(input())
a = list(map(int, input().split()))
for i in range(n):
    min = i
    for j in range(i+1, n):
        if a[j] < a[min]:
            min = j
    a[i], a[min] = a[min], a[i]
print(*a)
